highlights.text: Dangrangto has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “một bài hát không vui mấy - Extended Version” is the highest at #49.
“blue” by yung kai has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 163 days straight.
“All The Stars (with SZA) - From "Black Panther: The Album"” by Kendrick Lamar and SZA is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 22 spots at #72.
